WEBVTT

00:00:01.388 --> 00:00:04.563
Alright, let me tell you
about building synthetic cells

00:00:04.587 --> 00:00:06.532
and printing life.

00:00:06.556 --> 00:00:09.039
But first, let me tell you a quick story.

00:00:09.063 --> 00:00:11.569
On March 31, 2013,

00:00:11.593 --> 00:00:15.776
my team and I received an email
from an international health organization,

00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:18.633
alerting us that two men died in China

00:00:18.657 --> 00:00:21.712
shortly after contracting
the H7N9 bird flu.

00:00:22.149 --> 00:00:24.006
There were fears of a global pandemic

00:00:24.030 --> 00:00:27.363
as the virus started rapidly
moving across China.

00:00:28.004 --> 00:00:30.786
Although methods existed
to produce a flu vaccine